{"tid":1516704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"毒品調查科探員接報埋伏 休班警疑被搜出K仔今提堂","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:25:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a0eb8e4fcf50e1d906ca1d05d7dff9be37c16337","tid":1516704,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"警方毒品調查科探員今年接獲線報，於新屯門中心埋伏並截查三名男女，結果疑在其中一名休班警身上，搜出價值660元的1.3克氯胺酮（俗稱K仔）的毒品。休班警員被控項管有危險藥物罪，今天於屯門裁判法院提堂，辯方以需聘請私人律師為由，申請押後答辯，被告獲准以1,000元保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳天賜（46歲），控罪書上未有列出被告職業，控罪指他涉嫌於今年2月21日於新屯門中心3座地下電梯大堂，身上藏有兩個膠袋，內藏共1.3克粉末內含1.13克氯胺酮。<br />\n<br />\n據悉警方接獲線報及經調查後，於上址埋伏下將三人拘捕，案件押後至9月12日再提訊。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：TMCC 1769/19】<br />\n記者羅日昇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190829/59985924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F59985924&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=fb70523b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F59985924&h=ede3bf72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190829/59985924</a>"},{"pid":"a9a5ad1683526068fdf05e917a2eb6657f3177da","tid":1516704,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfZXgvh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfZXgvh.jpg&h=4847f4a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eba418053d4f2113010e8207c2bcb601ecf155aa","tid":1516704,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n831遊行<br />\n831<span style=\"color: red;\">死線</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWCh0Ky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWCh0